  "description": "<b>苹果前CEO斯科利（John&#160;Sculley）最近接受了CNBC的采访，他认为苹果在可穿戴设备领域有优势。</b><br /> 斯科利认为，可穿戴技术未来5-10年将对日常生活产生巨大影响，苹果在此领域有优势。斯科利说：“我觉得我们处在传感革命的起步点。可穿戴设备能让被动传感器监控许多不同的事物。”<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ccb79ab/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239742.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%89%8DCEO%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%9C%89%E4%BC%98%E5%8A%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239742.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%89%8DCEO%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%9C%89%E4%BC%98%E5%8A%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239742.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%89%8DCEO%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%9C%89%E4%BC%98%E5%8A%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239742.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%89%8DCEO%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%9C%89%E4%BC%98%E5%8A%BF\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239742.htm&amp;t=%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E5%89%8DCEO%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%AF%E7%A9%BF%E6%88%B4%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E8%8B%B9%E6%9E%9C%E6%9C%89%E4%BC%98%E5